Sentencas: An effective and facile technique has been developed for high temperature anode-electrolyte co-sintering of anode support solid oxide fuel cells by using microwave activated sparking plasma.
Titulo: An ultra-fast fabrication technique for anode support solid oxide fuel cells by microwave

Sentencas: A high sintering temperature of 1600 degrees C can be achieved in a few minutes time by discharging effect.
Titulo: An ultra-fast fabrication technique for anode support solid oxide fuel cells by microwave

Sentencas: Anode support substrate pellet is uniaxially pressed, and then dip-coated with a 10 mu m yttria stabilized zirconia electrolyte layer.
Titulo: An ultra-fast fabrication technique for anode support solid oxide fuel cells by microwave

Sentencas: After the microwave co-sintering, La0.8Sr0.2MnOx,, cathode is screen-printed onto electrolyte and sintered by conventional thermal method.
Titulo: An ultra-fast fabrication technique for anode support solid oxide fuel cells by microwave

Sentencas: The cell has stably operated in 3% humidified hydrogen for more than 130h.
Titulo: An ultra-fast fabrication technique for anode support solid oxide fuel cells by microwave
